# Regenerable board assets — the SOURCE (tokens.css, fonts.css, *.mjs,
# picks.json, README.md) is tracked; these are rebuilt by `node
# build-previews.mjs` + the subset recipe in README.md, and the boards also
# depend on the main checkout's git-excluded crate images, so they can't be
# re-rendered from a clone anyway. Keep the repo lean.
*/preview.html
*/fonts/
